        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-light mb-8 text-text">About Caelis Galeria</h1>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text">Caelis Galeria is a contemporary art gallery based in Shanghai, dedicated to presenting thoughtful artistic practices and cross-cultural perspectives. Founded with a vision to bridge Eastern and Western artistic dialogues, we focus on contemporary visual expression, critical discourse, and experimental approaches within an international context.</p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text">Our program encompasses solo and group exhibitions, artist residencies, publications, and public programs that engage with the most pressing questions of our time. We believe in the transformative power of art to challenge perceptions, foster understanding, and create space for contemplation.</p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-text">Located in the heart of Shanghai's cultural district, our 800-square-meter space provides an intimate yet expansive setting for experiencing contemporary art. We are committed to supporting both established and emerging artists whose work demonstrates exceptional artistic vision and conceptual rigor.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
